SDH: 
In SDH, monitoring is divided into section, line, and path levels. Section monitoring checks the physical link between adjacent nodes using RSOH. 
Line monitoring checks performance across multiplex sections using MSOH. 
Path monitoring ensures end-to-end data integrity using POH. Each level isolates faults at different parts of the network.”

